  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (Minimal profile)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. The model is applied to predict absolute hemolysis index for a Class III VAD at Model Risk Level 5 operating between 2500–4500 RPM and flow rates of 3–6 L/min. Intended use is pre-market submission support for a left-ventricular assist device; the patient population is adults with end-stage heart failure. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated; 7 achieved required levels and 6 remain as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification bounds shear-stress exposure predictions within ±18%. Decision: Accepted under the Minimal profile with acknowledged gaps documented in the decision record.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/vad-hemolysis-mrl5-req-001",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/vad-cfd-hemolysis-absolute-prediction",
